WEBVTT

00:01.702 --> 00:03.035
(lighter clinking)

00:29.330 --> 00:30.262
Junior.

00:30.331 --> 00:32.964
(door creaks open)

00:38.205 --> 00:40.805
(door creaking)

00:44.845 --> 00:47.079
(man whistling)

00:47.214 --> 00:48.680
Officer:
<i> See you next week.</i>

00:48.682 --> 00:51.649
(man whistling)
(door creaks open)

00:54.522 --> 01:00.625
(rhythmic drumming)

01:00.694 --> 01:01.960
(crowd cheering)

01:06.534 --> 01:07.966
These sons-of-bitches
act like they got a right

01:08.035 --> 01:09.434
To little we got.

01:09.436 --> 01:10.668
I should get going.

01:11.705 --> 01:13.372
I'm late for my revival
meeting as it is,

01:13.374 --> 01:15.707
And gwen's gonna
have a fit.

01:15.709 --> 01:17.342
You sure you don't
wanna stay with us?

01:17.378 --> 01:18.777
Or with me?

01:24.051 --> 01:26.017
Zeke, can you make
sure that my husband

01:26.053 --> 01:27.152
Stays out of
trouble tonight?

01:27.287 --> 01:28.454
Don't I always?

01:33.394 --> 01:34.859
(crowd cheering)

01:34.895 --> 01:40.799
(upbeat music)

01:40.934 --> 01:42.534
Courtesy of popsy,
with apologies.

01:42.570 --> 01:43.668
Thank you darling.

01:43.737 --> 01:44.736
You wanna
dance with me?

01:44.738 --> 01:45.937
Yes.

01:45.939 --> 01:48.206
(rhythmic saxophone and trumpet
music)

01:48.342 --> 01:55.247
(upbeat jazz music)

01:55.249 --> 02:05.323
♪

02:05.325 --> 02:15.300
♪

02:15.336 --> 02:25.210
♪

02:25.345 --> 02:35.320
♪

02:35.356 --> 02:40.459
♪

02:40.461 --> 02:45.397
(rhythmic drum solo)

02:58.512 --> 03:00.312
You missed a great
service last night.

03:00.447 --> 03:02.447
Mhm, I'm sure I'll
miss the next one too.

03:04.818 --> 03:07.285
How did I give my heart
away to such a heathen?

03:08.188 --> 03:09.888
Well, as I recall,
mrs. Massey,

03:11.158 --> 03:13.559
Last time I hear
you shout god,

03:13.694 --> 03:15.293
Wasn't a church in sight.

03:18.666 --> 03:21.433
(water splashing)

03:27.174 --> 03:28.306
Zeke:
<i> Hey junior,</i>

03:28.342 --> 03:29.974
<i> How late you planning</i>
<i> on making me?</i>

03:32.846 --> 03:34.513
Ms. Marlene.

03:34.515 --> 03:35.447
Good morning, zeke.

03:35.516 --> 03:36.914
Morning.

03:36.951 --> 03:38.650
<i> Henry's waiting</i>
<i> outside.</i>

03:38.686 --> 03:39.651
Alright teddy,

03:39.687 --> 03:41.086
Come and say goodbye
to your daddy.

03:42.690 --> 03:44.155
<i> Teddy.</i>

03:47.861 --> 03:50.828
Listen, I'll bring home a
little extra for the roof.

03:52.533 --> 03:53.831
<i> Come on.</i>

03:58.872 --> 04:01.540
Zeke:
<i> I didn't realize married</i>
<i> folks still had romance.</i>

04:01.542 --> 04:03.141
Junior:
<i> How 'bout you get</i>
<i> yourself a wife</i>

04:03.210 --> 04:04.610
<i> And come back to</i>
<i> me on that zeke.</i>

04:04.745 --> 04:07.345
Zeke:
<i> Well I am waiting for</i>
<i> that one special lady.</i>

04:07.381 --> 04:08.747
Junior:
<i> Alright.</i>

04:08.816 --> 04:10.348
Zeke:
<i> I mean, we can't all be as</i>
<i> lucky as junior massey.</i>

04:11.285 --> 04:12.884
Not luck me brotha,
just skill.

04:12.886 --> 04:14.018
Mhm.

04:14.054 --> 04:14.953
Henry, you getting
paid to wait there?

04:15.088 --> 04:16.521
Hey!
-Come on!

04:17.358 --> 04:18.356
When folks see
you read that,

04:18.492 --> 04:19.824
They gonna get ideas
about your ideas.

04:19.893 --> 04:21.159
Randolph knows
what's what.

04:21.228 --> 04:23.228
He really changed things
for the negro workers.

04:23.230 --> 04:24.963
S'why I'm going to take
the engineer's test.

04:26.433 --> 04:28.366
We cover their ass all the time
and don't get a dime for it.

04:28.402 --> 04:30.368
Figure I might as
well give it a shot.

04:31.438 --> 04:32.971
And you think they just
gon' walk in there

04:33.106 --> 04:34.172
And let you take it, huh?

04:34.174 --> 04:35.974
Randolph says the company
can't deny me taking it.

04:36.109 --> 04:38.310
Says if they try we'd have
cause for legal action.

04:38.445 --> 04:41.045
You gotta see the world with
the sun up henry, okay?!

04:41.081 --> 04:43.181
Hey, what he
mean to say is,

04:43.250 --> 04:45.383
White folk get real ugly
when they see a negro

04:45.519 --> 04:47.719
Aim to go from
the boy to a man.

04:47.755 --> 04:49.655
Learned that the
hard way.

04:51.525 --> 04:56.361
("pomp and pride" by
